## Part 2

```elixir
Day2.parse_input(day2) |> Enum.count(fn report -> 
  Day2.is_valid_report?(report) || report 
    |> Enum.with_index()
    |> Enum.any?(fn {_, i} -> 
      List.delete_at(report, i) 
      |> Day2.is_valid_report?() 
    end)
end)
```

